1) clone the repository

  * git clone git://github.com/ssavelan/django-school.git  

2) Fix up your settings.

cd django-school (or custom name)
mv empty_local_settings.py local_settings.py

open a Python Interpreter and run:

from random import choice
''.join([choice('abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789!@#$%^&*(-_=+)') for i in range(50)])
 
paste the result for your SECRET_KEY in local_settings.py

Set LIVE=False in your settings.py to run devel server with sqlite.

4) syncdb, runserver


